  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0d85\u0db8\u0dad\u0dbb-\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dc3\u0dca-\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba-\u2019\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7-\u0d8b\u0da9\u2019-\u0dba\u0db1-\u0dc4\u0dd0\u0da9/11-396554",
  "time_ut": 1661246918,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db8\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u2019\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7 \u0d8b\u0da9\u2019 \u0dba\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0da9",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Due to the loss of spare parts, the train is 'cut up'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Union of Railway Trade Unions says that it is becoming impossible to maintain the trains due to the lack of materials required to maintain the locomotives and carriages.",
        "It is said that due to various deficiencies in the engines that are currently running, those engines will have to be removed from running in a very short period of time, and about 20 engines have already had to be removed from running due to the lack of lubricants used in the daily engine repairs. Alliance points out.",
        "Also, due to the lack of spare parts required to maintain the engines, it has not been possible to carry out the repair work that should be done within the stipulated time. Due to this situation, nearly 50% of the engines have already been taken out of operation, said the alliance.",
        "Also, due to the lack of rails, sleepers, pandrol clips, nails, shoes and stones required for the railway, the railway has not been able to be maintained. Compared to other railways, the coastal railway is a railway that is difficult to maintain, and it is seen in a statement that more attention is requested for it.",
        "\"Though coated paints can be produced in the laboratory in the Ratmalana factory of the Railway Department, due to the lack of the required chemicals, it has not been possible to produce the paints. Due to this, it has not been possible to maintain the railway bridges in particular.",
        "Factory No. 43 has been closed due to lack of coal, Dematagoda Additional Road Maintenance Division has been closed due to vacancies of supervisory managers.",
        "In the face of all these circumstances, we would like to emphasize that the train is run by a dedicated group of employees and not by a management operation for the sake of a policy, purpose or goal. Let us also point out that even in the midst of the oppressive and dangerous situation facing the railways, the frauds, corruptions and irregularities are still happening and there is no intervention from the Ministry of Transport to stop them.",
        "Let us point out that even though the ministers issued various statements to gain political advantages, they are just boasts. It would be fruitless for the authorities to point the finger at the employees saying loss and loss despite the various avenues of income generation without paying any attention to them.",
        "Leaving aside all kinds of destruction, the government's readiness to restructure the railway department is strongly condemned, and it is very clear that railway privatization is not a solution to the government's dollar crisis, but a good railway service to the passengers.",
        "In this regard and many other matters, we request that you and the minister pay attention to it, so we request you to give us a date and time for it.''"
      ],
